HEADWORD: Laterad
<hw>Lat"er*ad</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>adv.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>latus</ets>, <ets>lateris</ets>, side + <ets>ad</ets> to.]</ety>
<fld>(Anat.)</fld> <def>Toward the side; away from the mesial plane; --
opposed to <ant>mesiad</ant>.</def>⟦br⟧
